com.ibm.team.build.common.notification

Class NotificationCriteriaFromBuildDefinition

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ibm.team.build.common.notification.NotificationCriteria
      • com.ibm.team.build.common.notification.NotificationCriteriaFromBuildDefinition

  • public class NotificationCriteriaFromBuildDefinition
extends NotificationCriteria
    Object used to store the criteria as to when and to whom email notifications should be sent for build lifecycle events. These objects are created from several configuration properties of the build definition's "Email Notification" configuration element.
    Since:
    0.8

    • Method Detail

      • getPropertyNamePrefixNumber

        public int getPropertyNamePrefixNumber()
        Returns:
        The number of the property that this criteria corresponds to. For example, if this criteria were the first one saved in a build definition, it would receive the number "0" since the prefix used to store preferences is "com.ibm.team.build.email.criteria.0".
